ygData.messageBody:
Want in on a little secret? A large race SK is one of the most useful and
most powerful tanks in the game, and shows his true nature after level 35...
He can tank almost as good as a warr, pull almost as good as a monk, and is
fd pulling the lord room while the warriors are shouting for a invis at
zone... Alot of guilds on my server are going with SK in the planes as
well...
IMO they are the best tank in game hands down..
